WEBVTT

00:01:40.610 --> 00:01:46.000
[THE DEVIL BETWEEN US]

00:01:46.030 --> 00:01:48.990
[Episode 14]

00:02:12.030 --> 00:02:12.660
Dad.

00:02:14.480 --> 00:02:15.040
Mr. Hu.

00:02:15.070 --> 00:02:15.840
Wenjing?

00:02:16.680 --> 00:02:17.540
Jin, you're here too.

00:02:17.540 --> 00:02:18.360
You go upstairs first.

00:02:18.360 --> 00:02:19.560
Okay, I'm heading up.

00:02:19.930 --> 00:02:20.520
Okay.

00:02:21.710 --> 00:02:22.240
What...

00:02:22.310 --> 00:02:23.150
What are you doing here?

00:02:23.150 --> 00:02:24.190
Why are you back?

00:02:24.320 --> 00:02:25.730
Weren't you in the city?

00:02:27.130 --> 00:02:28.530
We're working on a case here.

00:02:28.530 --> 00:02:29.810
This is our base.

00:02:31.520 --> 00:02:32.190
Here?

00:02:34.470 --> 00:02:36.310
Wait, didn't you go
to the Archives Division?

00:02:36.310 --> 00:02:38.240
Why are you still working on cases?

00:02:38.790 --> 00:02:40.090
I didn't go to Archives Division.

00:02:40.090 --> 00:02:41.890
I joined the Narcotics Brigade.

00:02:41.910 --> 00:02:42.590
What?

00:02:43.280 --> 00:02:44.470
Narcotics Brigade?

00:02:51.240 --> 00:02:53.370
I've told you everything I need to say.

00:02:53.890 --> 00:02:55.090
Don't just sit there.

00:02:55.150 --> 00:02:55.870
Pack up.

00:02:55.870 --> 00:02:57.200
We leave tomorrow morning.

00:02:57.200 --> 00:02:58.800
The police will find us soon.

00:03:00.270 --> 00:03:01.960
Don't rush me. Let me think.

00:03:02.040 --> 00:03:03.360
What is there to think about?

00:03:03.360 --> 00:03:05.020
We are risking our necks here.

00:03:05.200 --> 00:03:06.990
Once the police suspect us
through Cheng Ken,

00:03:06.990 --> 00:03:07.990
you are finished.

00:03:13.150 --> 00:03:14.210
Cheng Ken is right.

00:03:16.240 --> 00:03:18.100
We haven't made enough money yet.

00:03:21.829 --> 00:03:22.829
Are you two crazy?

00:03:26.480 --> 00:03:27.430
Go tell him

00:03:28.200 --> 00:03:29.360
if he gets caught,

00:03:29.920 --> 00:03:31.200
as long as we get abroad,

00:03:31.200 --> 00:03:32.360
I will immediately

00:03:32.430 --> 00:03:33.760
give all the money he deserves

00:03:33.760 --> 00:03:35.110
to someone he trusts.

00:03:35.110 --> 00:03:37.550
All that money will be used for Jiajia.

00:03:38.240 --> 00:03:39.270
Tell him not to worry.

00:03:39.270 --> 00:03:41.040
Just focus wholeheartedly

00:03:41.100 --> 00:03:42.150
on buying us time.

00:03:42.150 --> 00:03:43.010
Can you do that?

00:03:43.079 --> 00:03:45.200
You always thought Cheng Ken was a fool.

00:03:45.200 --> 00:03:46.829
Can he fool the police?

00:03:49.520 --> 00:03:51.270
Then this is the only bet I can make.

00:03:51.270 --> 00:03:52.600
What if you lose the bet?

00:03:52.870 --> 00:03:54.329
It's your life on the line.

00:03:55.040 --> 00:03:57.430
There are more people
made greedy by money

00:03:57.430 --> 00:03:59.920
than people made rich by greed.

00:04:03.960 --> 00:04:05.080
Haven't our lives

00:04:05.230 --> 00:04:07.160
always been on the gambling table?

00:04:25.150 --> 00:04:26.080
Xiaodong.

00:04:28.590 --> 00:04:30.350
It's really nice out tonight.

00:04:32.760 --> 00:04:34.120
Take a walk with me.

00:04:34.200 --> 00:04:34.390
Okay.

00:04:34.390 --> 00:04:35.070
Thank you.

00:04:38.560 --> 00:04:39.270
Oh, you.

00:04:40.030 --> 00:04:42.230
I don't object to you having ambitions.

00:04:42.250 --> 00:04:44.690
But you have to remember
you have children at home.

00:04:44.690 --> 00:04:47.220
Ming and Zhi are still at home
waiting for you.

00:04:47.270 --> 00:04:47.909
I know.

00:04:47.909 --> 00:04:48.760
How could I forget?

00:04:48.760 --> 00:04:50.590
I video call them every few days.

00:04:51.120 --> 00:04:52.190
Is that the same?

00:04:52.220 --> 00:04:54.590
You haven't been back
for over a week again.

00:04:54.590 --> 00:04:55.320
I just wonder,

00:04:55.320 --> 00:04:56.650
don't you miss the kids?

00:05:00.200 --> 00:05:01.200
I know.

00:05:01.520 --> 00:05:02.350
My daughter is all grown up.

00:05:02.350 --> 00:05:03.640
She doesn't listen to her dad anymore.

00:05:03.640 --> 00:05:04.970
I won't nag you anymore.

00:05:05.170 --> 00:05:07.100
Just handle things well yourself.

00:05:07.270 --> 00:05:08.680
But remember one thing.

00:05:09.080 --> 00:05:11.320
You must be very, very careful.

00:05:11.340 --> 00:05:12.470
I know. Don't worry.

00:05:13.200 --> 00:05:13.910
Okay.

00:05:14.640 --> 00:05:16.030
Don't worry about home.

00:05:16.030 --> 00:05:17.750
I'll take care of the kids for you.

00:05:17.750 --> 00:05:19.640
I can't change your mind anyway.

00:05:20.030 --> 00:05:21.390
The only thing I can do

00:05:21.390 --> 00:05:23.790
is to provide you with backup support.

00:05:24.440 --> 00:05:25.440
That's so touching.

00:05:25.440 --> 00:05:26.120
Really touching.

00:05:26.120 --> 00:05:27.320
Thanks, Mr. Hu.

00:05:27.390 --> 00:05:28.880
You're just all talk.

00:05:29.680 --> 00:05:31.960
By the way, why are you
hanging around here at this time?

00:05:31.960 --> 00:05:32.760
This street is full of...

00:05:32.760 --> 00:05:33.470
you know, that stuff.

00:05:33.470 --> 00:05:34.150
It's all that stuff.

00:05:34.150 --> 00:05:35.320
Just out for a stroll.

00:05:35.320 --> 00:05:36.590
I was just passing by.

00:05:36.590 --> 00:05:37.200
I'm heading back now.

00:05:37.200 --> 00:05:38.080
You can't keep...

00:05:38.080 --> 00:05:39.200
You go do your thing.

00:05:39.200 --> 00:05:39.880
I'm going back.

00:05:39.880 --> 00:05:41.010
Go on with your work.

00:05:41.390 --> 00:05:42.230
Take care.

00:05:59.470 --> 00:06:01.130
Nuanfeng No. 1 Middle School.

00:06:01.350 --> 00:06:02.350
My alma mater.

00:06:03.880 --> 00:06:05.280
Hu Wenjing and Wang Ping.

00:06:06.080 --> 00:06:07.400
I met them right here.

00:06:08.790 --> 00:06:10.230
Do you know how we met?

00:06:10.930 --> 00:06:12.160
You never told me.

00:06:15.420 --> 00:06:16.220
Sir,

00:06:17.000 --> 00:06:18.530
one Maochuan Spicy Hot Pot.

00:06:18.640 --> 00:06:19.570
Coming right up.

00:06:22.100 --> 00:06:23.900
The first time I saw Hu Wenjing,

00:06:24.710 --> 00:06:26.120
I was drawn to her.

00:06:27.680 --> 00:06:28.790
She...

00:06:31.230 --> 00:06:32.230
didn't talk much.

00:06:32.640 --> 00:06:33.590
She was real.

00:06:36.970 --> 00:06:37.670
As for me,

00:06:38.790 --> 00:06:40.909
I was always trying to get to know her.

00:06:42.120 --> 00:06:44.650
Just like how you're
trying to get close to me.

00:06:47.350 --> 00:06:49.409
Wang Ping was Hu Wenjing's deskmate.

00:06:49.700 --> 00:06:50.820
They were closer.

00:06:51.880 --> 00:06:52.880
I kept thinking about

00:06:52.880 --> 00:06:54.210
how to join their group.

00:06:54.790 --> 00:06:55.710
Unexpectedly,

00:06:55.790 --> 00:06:57.190
I actually did join them.

00:06:57.530 --> 00:06:58.650
But even now,

00:06:59.390 --> 00:07:01.200
those two are still a bit closer.

00:07:01.860 --> 00:07:03.390
You three are best friends,

00:07:03.410 --> 00:07:05.340
yet you still rank your closeness?

00:07:05.790 --> 00:07:06.830
Of course.

00:07:09.120 --> 00:07:10.320
Maybe I've just

00:07:11.320 --> 00:07:14.050
always admired strong people
since I was little.

00:07:15.080 --> 00:07:15.880
Hu Wenjing

00:07:16.830 --> 00:07:17.710
had good grades

00:07:18.390 --> 00:07:19.320
and was popular.

00:07:21.470 --> 00:07:23.870
I wanted to compete
with her in everything.

00:07:24.390 --> 00:07:26.520
And she was always willing to respond.

00:07:26.710 --> 00:07:27.320
Usually,

00:07:27.470 --> 00:07:28.560
at times like that,

00:07:29.030 --> 00:07:29.910
Wang Ping

00:07:30.440 --> 00:07:31.370
was the referee.

00:07:35.880 --> 00:07:36.560
Start.

00:07:58.440 --> 00:07:59.320
I give up.

00:08:01.120 --> 00:08:02.320
Wenjing drank water.

00:08:02.320 --> 00:08:03.570
Li Xiaoya wins.

00:08:05.960 --> 00:08:06.830
Don't drink it all.

00:08:06.830 --> 00:08:07.760
Save some for me.

00:08:08.520 --> 00:08:09.780
Hurry, I'm burning up.

00:08:10.200 --> 00:08:11.200
I want some too.

00:08:11.560 --> 00:08:12.250
Hurry.

00:08:19.230 --> 00:08:20.270
In a competition,

00:08:20.590 --> 00:08:22.220
it's normal to win or lose.

00:08:23.090 --> 00:08:23.970
But this time,

00:08:25.590 --> 00:08:26.710
I must win.

00:08:30.520 --> 00:08:33.250
Why do you always
want to compete with Hu Wenjing?

00:08:33.830 --> 00:08:35.690
Besides, there's no referee now.

00:08:36.080 --> 00:08:37.610
Is there really no referee?

00:08:40.400 --> 00:08:43.400
Everyone in Nuanfeng County
who knows me is a referee.

00:08:43.590 --> 00:08:44.800
How they see me

00:08:45.320 --> 00:08:46.780
is the result of the match.

00:08:50.080 --> 00:08:52.610
When I left
the county radio station back then,

00:08:52.610 --> 00:08:53.760
I swore an oath.

00:08:54.110 --> 00:08:55.040
In this life,

00:08:55.710 --> 00:08:57.990
I must make lots and lots of money.

00:08:58.350 --> 00:09:00.150
I must be extremely successful.

00:09:00.440 --> 00:09:02.180
I want everyone to envy me.

00:09:03.080 --> 00:09:04.710
Then I'll take all that money,

00:09:04.710 --> 00:09:05.710
and leave.

00:09:06.320 --> 00:09:07.400
I'll go away,

00:09:07.880 --> 00:09:08.940
make a fresh start,

00:09:11.200 --> 00:09:12.800
and then I'll truly have won.

00:09:14.690 --> 00:09:16.950
Why do you always care what others think?

00:09:17.830 --> 00:09:19.430
Do you live for other people?

00:09:19.470 --> 00:09:20.470
Who doesn't care?

00:09:22.320 --> 00:09:23.280
Don't you care?

00:09:26.440 --> 00:09:29.080
You don't care
because you won't admit you do.

00:09:29.270 --> 00:09:31.200
Because you're cowardly and weak.

00:09:32.630 --> 00:09:34.630
But in this life, I

00:09:35.530 --> 00:09:37.410
will never be a weakling.

00:09:40.510 --> 00:09:41.290
Honey,

00:09:43.620 --> 00:09:45.220
I want you to be like me.

00:09:47.580 --> 00:09:50.010
Only when we truly become the strong ones,

00:09:51.080 --> 00:09:52.440
can we truly not care

00:09:52.440 --> 00:09:53.840
about what others think.

00:09:54.870 --> 00:09:57.000
As long as we hold on for one more night,

00:09:57.990 --> 00:10:00.390
we can make several hundred thousand more.

00:10:00.670 --> 00:10:01.830
Do you know how many people right now

00:10:01.830 --> 00:10:03.230
are begging me for agency rights,

00:10:03.230 --> 00:10:04.710
begging me to let them franchise?

00:10:04.710 --> 00:10:06.830
The fields are full of crops.

00:10:08.160 --> 00:10:09.360
Not harvesting them,

00:10:11.080 --> 00:10:12.280
how is that possible?

00:10:25.350 --> 00:10:27.350
Cheng Ken can't hold on much longer.

00:10:29.160 --> 00:10:29.960
I know.

00:10:31.970 --> 00:10:32.760
Don't worry.

00:10:33.870 --> 00:10:34.800
I still have a way

00:10:36.680 --> 00:10:38.810
to give us an extra layer of insurance.

00:10:47.280 --> 00:10:49.080
Let's go over this again.

00:10:49.080 --> 00:10:50.470
When Cheng Ken

00:10:50.720 --> 00:10:52.720
was caught at the bar,

00:10:52.990 --> 00:10:55.160
the milk tea shop hadn't been exposed yet.

00:10:55.160 --> 00:10:55.680
Right?

00:10:55.830 --> 00:10:57.510
Let's confirm again that Cheng Ken

00:10:57.510 --> 00:10:58.710
actually has nothing to do

00:10:58.710 --> 00:11:00.230
with this group.

00:11:00.330 --> 00:11:01.730
Didn't we say before that

00:11:01.960 --> 00:11:04.020
we doubt the man in black is Cheng Ken?

00:11:04.210 --> 00:11:06.160
I'm telling you, ten to one, he is.

00:11:07.800 --> 00:11:08.590
I still feel like

00:11:08.590 --> 00:11:11.400
Cheng Ken didn't come
to buy drugs from Lv Deli.

00:11:11.870 --> 00:11:14.830
If he was not buying drugs,
then what was he doing?

00:11:14.920 --> 00:11:16.110
Not buying drugs...

00:11:21.230 --> 00:11:23.030
He's heading towards the river.

00:11:29.400 --> 00:11:29.870
Here he comes.

00:11:29.870 --> 00:11:30.630
Cheng Ken

00:11:30.920 --> 00:11:32.320
and Lv Deli.

00:11:32.320 --> 00:11:33.280
Let me think.

00:11:34.320 --> 00:11:36.160
Cheng Ken and Lv Deli.

00:11:59.710 --> 00:12:00.560
In there.

00:12:04.110 --> 00:12:04.870
Okay.

00:12:05.590 --> 00:12:06.590
Keep an eye on her.

00:12:07.160 --> 00:12:08.160
I'll be back soon.

00:12:11.990 --> 00:12:12.460
Let's go.

00:12:12.460 --> 00:12:13.190
Come with me.

00:12:23.320 --> 00:12:25.040
He brought the girl here.

00:12:25.280 --> 00:12:26.350
He took her away.

00:12:26.750 --> 00:12:27.470
Right?

00:12:27.470 --> 00:12:28.710
He didn't come to buy drugs.

00:12:28.710 --> 00:12:29.750
He came to buy a human.

00:12:29.750 --> 00:12:30.710
He took a person.

00:12:30.710 --> 00:12:31.200
Right?

00:12:31.280 --> 00:12:32.280
Why would he buy a person?

00:12:32.280 --> 00:12:33.210
He wants organs.

00:12:33.750 --> 00:12:34.990
His daughter needs
a kidney right now, doesn't she?

00:12:34.990 --> 00:12:36.200
To give Jiajia a transplant.

00:12:36.200 --> 00:12:37.710
Is it possible he sought him out
to buy this person?

00:12:37.710 --> 00:12:39.680
He planted the drugs on her.

00:12:39.870 --> 00:12:41.350
So after he ended up with the drugs,

00:12:41.350 --> 00:12:42.230
he didn't know what to do.

00:12:42.230 --> 00:12:43.870
He couldn't sell them anywhere,

00:12:43.870 --> 00:12:45.470
so he's just wandering around.

00:12:45.470 --> 00:12:45.990
Yes.

00:12:54.590 --> 00:12:55.510
Okay, I got it.

00:12:55.510 --> 00:12:56.280
Thanks.

00:12:57.400 --> 00:12:58.350
Exactly.

00:12:58.350 --> 00:12:59.470
The logic holds up.

00:12:59.800 --> 00:13:00.400
It must be this.

00:13:00.400 --> 00:13:01.080
That has to be it.

00:13:01.080 --> 00:13:02.630
Cheng Ken just bought a ticket online.

00:13:02.630 --> 00:13:05.760
A train ticket to Lincang, Chunzhou,
for 4 days from now.

00:13:15.680 --> 00:13:17.800
I came to find you because I have an idea.

00:13:17.800 --> 00:13:19.830
Cao Jinchuan told me

00:13:19.930 --> 00:13:21.530
there's someone in Chunzhou

00:13:21.570 --> 00:13:22.800
who wants to buy my goods.

00:13:22.800 --> 00:13:24.320
Whether it's true or not,

00:13:25.800 --> 00:13:26.950
we might be able to

00:13:27.550 --> 00:13:29.080
use this to our advantage.

00:13:29.440 --> 00:13:31.630
With the police,

00:13:31.630 --> 00:13:33.870
we can fabricate a buyer in Chunzhou.

00:13:34.590 --> 00:13:35.830
This will distract them

00:13:35.830 --> 00:13:37.510
and lead them on a wild goose chase

00:13:37.510 --> 00:13:38.280
to buy the two of you

00:13:38.280 --> 00:13:39.030
more time to move the goods.

00:13:39.030 --> 00:13:39.830
[2024 Vitality Curve
Franchisee Conference]

00:13:39.830 --> 00:13:40.640
[Keynote Speaker: Ms. Li Xiaoya]

00:13:40.670 --> 00:13:41.990
[2024 Vitality Curve
Franchisee Conference]

00:13:42.410 --> 00:13:44.440
Every extra day we stay here

00:13:44.470 --> 00:13:46.280
adds more risk, Ken.

00:13:46.330 --> 00:13:47.860
But we also make more money.

00:13:49.690 --> 00:13:50.620
I need money.

00:13:54.270 --> 00:13:55.390
You need money too.

00:13:57.440 --> 00:13:59.680
From being scammed
to reaching the peak again,

00:13:59.680 --> 00:14:01.110
how many days did it take me?

00:14:01.110 --> 00:14:02.440
Seven days.

00:14:02.510 --> 00:14:03.280
That's right.

00:14:03.280 --> 00:14:05.420
Compared to the creation
of the world by God...

00:14:05.420 --> 00:14:06.510
I've seen you.

00:14:07.120 --> 00:14:08.840
You're the man behind Xiaoya.

00:14:10.440 --> 00:14:11.560
I am nothing.

00:14:12.470 --> 00:14:14.070
Xiaoya did it all by herself.

00:14:14.350 --> 00:14:15.230
Seven days

00:14:16.350 --> 00:14:18.590
made a new me.

00:14:19.400 --> 00:14:20.510
Give it a month,

00:14:21.560 --> 00:14:23.870
and 100 of you can be just like me!

00:14:24.400 --> 00:14:25.400
Don't worry, Xiaoya.

00:14:25.400 --> 00:14:26.110
Give me two days.

00:14:26.110 --> 00:14:27.080
Two days is enough.

00:14:27.080 --> 00:14:29.400
I will arrange the shipment
as fast as possible.

00:14:29.400 --> 00:14:30.470
Now, please welcome my

00:14:30.470 --> 00:14:32.470
first partner, Hua.

00:14:38.510 --> 00:14:39.350
First,

00:14:39.710 --> 00:14:41.560
I want to thank Xiaoya.

00:14:42.400 --> 00:14:43.400
Thank her

00:14:43.750 --> 00:14:46.550
for giving me this opportunity
to make easy money.

00:14:47.750 --> 00:14:50.290
We have always been good friends.

00:15:09.320 --> 00:15:10.470
I'm not afraid of anything else.

00:15:10.470 --> 00:15:13.000
I'm just afraid
Jiajia won't get her surgery.

00:15:13.960 --> 00:15:15.160
Promise me one thing.

00:15:17.180 --> 00:15:18.710
If something happens to me,

00:15:20.030 --> 00:15:21.410
take my share of the money

00:15:21.410 --> 00:15:22.810
and give it to Jiajia.

00:15:25.560 --> 00:15:26.290
Don't worry.

00:15:27.350 --> 00:15:28.830
Jiajia is my niece.

00:15:34.900 --> 00:15:36.140
Anything else?

00:15:40.230 --> 00:15:40.800
No.

00:16:00.490 --> 00:16:01.500
Hello, here is the menu.

00:16:01.500 --> 00:16:02.300
Okay, thanks.

00:16:05.320 --> 00:16:07.050
Have we seen that woman before?

00:16:07.280 --> 00:16:08.070
No.

00:16:09.870 --> 00:16:11.530
What's he signing over there?

00:16:19.430 --> 00:16:20.160
Why...

00:16:20.590 --> 00:16:21.280
Why is he leaving?

00:16:21.280 --> 00:16:22.810
I just ordered this coffee.

00:16:23.870 --> 00:16:24.420
Forget it.

00:16:24.420 --> 00:16:25.510
Call you later.

00:16:26.420 --> 00:16:27.150
I'm leaving.

00:16:33.590 --> 00:16:34.440
Hello.

00:16:34.680 --> 00:16:35.280
Hello.

00:16:35.280 --> 00:16:36.280
Who are you?

00:16:36.560 --> 00:16:37.350
Police.

00:16:38.000 --> 00:16:39.150
Is something wrong?

00:16:39.180 --> 00:16:41.310
What did that person talk to you about?

00:16:56.340 --> 00:17:00.050
[Jin Longzheng]

00:17:00.050 --> 00:17:00.580
Wenjing.

00:17:00.710 --> 00:17:01.510
I found out.

00:17:01.830 --> 00:17:03.200
Cheng Ken bought 2 insurance policies.

00:17:03.200 --> 00:17:04.400
One personal accident insurance,

00:17:04.400 --> 00:17:06.329
and a short-term accident policy.

00:17:07.069 --> 00:17:07.680
Okay. Where are you?

00:17:07.680 --> 00:17:08.710
I'll come find you.

00:17:08.710 --> 00:17:10.240
I'll send you the location.

00:17:14.270 --> 00:17:15.470
Insurance.

00:17:49.440 --> 00:17:50.800
Here. Here.

00:18:07.500 --> 00:18:08.260
Hua,

00:18:08.580 --> 00:18:09.930
pleasure working with you.

00:18:09.930 --> 00:18:11.930
Pleasure working with you, Xiaoya.

00:18:14.600 --> 00:18:15.670
Where are you?

00:18:20.390 --> 00:18:21.080
Bye.

00:18:29.920 --> 00:18:30.710
I see him.

00:18:30.710 --> 00:18:31.630
I'll stop here.

00:18:36.470 --> 00:18:37.230
It's quite windy.

00:18:37.230 --> 00:18:37.840
It's fine.

00:18:41.990 --> 00:18:42.790
Alright then.

00:18:42.790 --> 00:18:44.310
I'll go say hello in a bit.

00:18:44.310 --> 00:18:45.120
Go ahead.

00:19:03.920 --> 00:19:04.750
Li Xiaoya.

00:19:06.440 --> 00:19:07.270
Wenjing?

00:19:08.160 --> 00:19:09.440
What are you doing here?

00:19:09.440 --> 00:19:10.710
I was passing by on business.

00:19:10.710 --> 00:19:12.040
What're you doing here?

00:19:12.710 --> 00:19:14.750
I thought you got the news
and came to see me.

00:19:14.750 --> 00:19:16.270
I'm holding a product launch here.

00:19:16.270 --> 00:19:17.360
I saw your WeChat Moments.

00:19:17.360 --> 00:19:17.790
Good.

00:19:17.790 --> 00:19:19.080
You business is booming.

00:19:19.080 --> 00:19:19.660
It's alright.

00:19:19.660 --> 00:19:20.920
They want to say hello.

00:19:20.990 --> 00:19:21.960
Xiaoya, we're leaving now.

00:19:21.960 --> 00:19:22.400
We're leaving.

00:19:22.400 --> 00:19:22.790
Bye.

00:19:22.790 --> 00:19:23.160
Bye.

00:19:23.360 --> 00:19:23.960
Bye.

00:19:25.470 --> 00:19:27.930
That was Cheng Ken
who came to see you, right?

00:19:28.360 --> 00:19:29.220
What did he say?

00:19:29.580 --> 00:19:31.360
He said he's going away for a few days.

00:19:31.360 --> 00:19:33.400
He's leaving the child at his mom's place,

00:19:33.400 --> 00:19:34.140
and asked us to keep an eye on her.

00:19:34.140 --> 00:19:34.870
For how long?

00:19:35.270 --> 00:19:36.870
How many days will he be gone?

00:19:39.080 --> 00:19:39.950
Four days.

00:19:40.710 --> 00:19:41.160
Okay.

00:19:41.450 --> 00:19:42.990
Is Cheng Ken in some kind of trouble?

00:19:42.990 --> 00:19:43.310
No.

00:19:43.310 --> 00:19:43.880
It's a case.

00:19:43.880 --> 00:19:44.750
He's a witness.

00:19:44.750 --> 00:19:46.200
We're protecting him in secret.

00:19:46.200 --> 00:19:46.840
A witness?

00:19:46.840 --> 00:19:47.680
Is he in danger?

00:19:47.680 --> 00:19:48.280
No danger.

00:19:48.280 --> 00:19:49.840
We've identified the suspects.

00:19:49.840 --> 00:19:52.570
The bad guys will definitely
be caught in the end.

00:19:52.640 --> 00:19:53.710
I mean, if he comes to find you again

00:19:53.710 --> 00:19:54.550
later on,

00:19:54.550 --> 00:19:55.230
or tells you anything,

00:19:55.230 --> 00:19:56.830
give me a call and let me know.

00:19:56.920 --> 00:19:57.550
Sure, no problem.

00:19:57.550 --> 00:19:58.070
Alright, get back to work.

00:19:58.070 --> 00:19:58.680
I have nothing else.

00:19:58.680 --> 00:19:59.360
Bye.

00:19:59.470 --> 00:20:00.120
Wenjing.

00:20:01.360 --> 00:20:02.550
How is Wang Ping?

00:20:02.680 --> 00:20:04.360
Wang Ping is getting out of

00:20:04.640 --> 00:20:05.790
the rehab center tomorrow.

00:20:05.790 --> 00:20:06.680
But I have something to do tomorrow,

00:20:06.680 --> 00:20:07.880
so I might not be able
to pick her up in time.

00:20:07.880 --> 00:20:09.540
If you're free, go pick her up.

00:20:09.790 --> 00:20:10.680
Don't look at me.

00:20:10.680 --> 00:20:11.230
Hua...

00:20:11.230 --> 00:20:12.270
I didn't ask you to go.

00:20:12.270 --> 00:20:12.920
I'll go.

00:20:13.030 --> 00:20:13.710
I'm free.

00:20:13.710 --> 00:20:14.920
Alright, if I finish early,

00:20:14.920 --> 00:20:15.750
I'll come meet up with you.

00:20:15.750 --> 00:20:16.030
Okay.

00:20:16.030 --> 00:20:16.400
Get busy.

00:20:16.400 --> 00:20:16.790
I'm off.

00:20:16.790 --> 00:20:17.310
Bye.

00:20:20.970 --> 00:20:22.010
Can we fool her?

00:20:25.170 --> 00:20:27.240
The more Cheng Ken entrusts
the child to us,

00:20:27.240 --> 00:20:29.840
the more it shows
we have nothing to do with him.

00:20:29.950 --> 00:20:30.800
Besides,

00:20:31.310 --> 00:20:33.440
we probably won't have to lie for long.

00:21:04.360 --> 00:21:05.440
How much?

00:21:20.390 --> 00:21:21.250
Twenty-three.

00:21:59.190 --> 00:22:00.340
Open an account for me.

00:22:00.340 --> 00:22:01.210
Charge 30.

00:22:39.070 --> 00:22:40.680
[Exchange with stones]

00:22:40.680 --> 00:22:42.030
[Chunzhou]

00:22:42.030 --> 00:22:43.120
[Battle of Red Cliff; Fourth Day]

00:22:43.140 --> 00:22:44.460
[150W]

00:24:04.790 --> 00:24:05.990
You've got long legs,

00:24:06.170 --> 00:24:07.430
but you don't run fast.

00:24:14.840 --> 00:24:15.920
I'm injured.

00:24:18.280 --> 00:24:19.320
How did it happen?

00:24:21.790 --> 00:24:22.650
I took a bullet.

00:24:32.390 --> 00:24:33.790
What does that feel like?

00:24:35.880 --> 00:24:36.940
I didn't feel much.

00:24:38.750 --> 00:24:40.030
It felt like

00:24:40.110 --> 00:24:41.640
getting an electric shock.

00:24:42.550 --> 00:24:44.160
It didn't hurt at first.

00:24:44.500 --> 00:24:46.630
Can you give me and my daughter a break?

00:24:53.310 --> 00:24:53.950
Sure.

00:24:57.030 --> 00:24:58.830
Come back to the station with me.

00:25:00.040 --> 00:25:01.900
Confess everything you've done.

00:25:04.470 --> 00:25:05.470
I confess...

00:25:09.120 --> 00:25:10.230
Confess what?

00:25:11.600 --> 00:25:13.000
I haven't done anything.

00:25:26.370 --> 00:25:27.290
Ken.

00:25:29.550 --> 00:25:32.350
I can help you raise money
within the police force,

00:25:32.430 --> 00:25:34.760
and I can help you fundraise publicly too.

00:25:34.990 --> 00:25:36.160
We'll figure it out together.

00:25:36.160 --> 00:25:37.690
We'll cure Jiajia for sure.

00:25:38.920 --> 00:25:40.320
When Jiajia gets better,

00:25:40.750 --> 00:25:41.750
with your experience,

00:25:41.750 --> 00:25:44.600
it won't be hard
to find another accounting job, right?

00:25:44.600 --> 00:25:46.660
Isn't it good to live a peaceful life?

00:25:51.960 --> 00:25:53.160
You are a good person.

00:25:53.640 --> 00:25:54.600
So are you.

00:25:55.430 --> 00:25:57.760
Don't forget, I investigated you before.

00:25:58.960 --> 00:26:00.460
You're just under too much pressure.

00:26:00.460 --> 00:26:02.320
Yes, I am under too much pressure.

00:26:06.550 --> 00:26:08.210
So I need to get some fresh air,

00:26:08.310 --> 00:26:09.200
go for a run,

00:26:11.360 --> 00:26:12.420
and exercise a bit.

00:26:17.640 --> 00:26:18.840
I'm done exercising.

00:26:20.550 --> 00:26:21.880
You can get off work now.

00:26:24.160 --> 00:26:25.820
Let's run together sometime.

00:26:28.680 --> 00:26:31.140
Once I recover,
you won't be able to run away.

00:26:32.390 --> 00:26:33.600
If you can outrun me,

00:26:34.070 --> 00:26:35.800
you have to take care of Jiajia.

00:27:37.310 --> 00:27:38.200
Kai.

00:27:38.880 --> 00:27:40.160
Let's rest where we are.

00:27:40.160 --> 00:27:41.750
Get out and stretch your legs.

00:27:41.750 --> 00:27:43.950
Go get a few more
boxed meals from Liu's.

00:27:44.440 --> 00:27:45.550
I'll have the pork
with garlic scapes again.

00:27:45.550 --> 00:27:46.810
Chili and eggs for him.

00:27:47.200 --> 00:27:49.400
And get some pickles or something.

00:27:49.840 --> 00:27:50.770
The usual place.

00:27:51.310 --> 00:27:52.120
Roger that.

00:27:59.360 --> 00:28:00.440
Hypothetically,

00:28:00.750 --> 00:28:03.070
if he's really going
to Chunzhou for a deal,

00:28:03.070 --> 00:28:05.310
and we pin him down
before he gets on the bus,

00:28:05.310 --> 00:28:06.990
will we find that batch of drugs?

00:28:06.990 --> 00:28:07.790
What I'm afraid of is

00:28:07.790 --> 00:28:09.600
that he's already sold the drugs,

00:28:09.600 --> 00:28:10.670
hidden the money,

00:28:11.070 --> 00:28:12.030
and is just acting now.

00:28:12.030 --> 00:28:12.680
Maybe he's playing us.

00:28:12.680 --> 00:28:13.400
Walking us like dogs.

00:28:13.400 --> 00:28:14.730
Him in front, us behind.

00:28:15.830 --> 00:28:17.470
His goal is to shake us off,

00:28:18.230 --> 00:28:19.270
and take his daughter away.

00:28:19.270 --> 00:28:20.580
Isn't that what's happening?

00:28:20.580 --> 00:28:22.710
So we need to watch him even closer now.

00:28:24.070 --> 00:28:25.790
This means 24-hour standby.

00:28:25.850 --> 00:28:27.570
Neither of us is going home.

00:28:31.750 --> 00:28:32.480
So annoying.

00:28:34.550 --> 00:28:35.550
Drink some water.

00:28:37.770 --> 00:28:38.890
Am I out of water?

00:28:40.270 --> 00:28:42.310
You're out of water. Will you drink mine?

00:28:42.310 --> 00:28:43.240
I'm not thirsty.

00:28:56.990 --> 00:28:57.880
I'm going out.

00:28:58.710 --> 00:28:59.640
Dad.

00:29:01.430 --> 00:29:04.510
You're frowning so much.

00:29:06.550 --> 00:29:07.070
Really?

00:29:08.310 --> 00:29:09.920
Everything will be fine.

00:29:11.120 --> 00:29:12.520
Everything will be fine.

00:29:16.520 --> 00:29:17.280
Later,

00:29:17.750 --> 00:29:18.920
after the dialysis,

00:29:19.990 --> 00:29:20.960
the two of us

00:29:21.290 --> 00:29:22.420
will go out for a bit.

00:29:23.400 --> 00:29:24.550
Where to?

00:29:26.310 --> 00:29:27.440
I'll think about it.

00:29:37.200 --> 00:29:38.640
You haven't slept all night?

00:29:38.640 --> 00:29:39.230
No.

00:29:39.470 --> 00:29:39.960
Okay.

00:29:40.360 --> 00:29:40.880
Go back

00:29:41.030 --> 00:29:41.600
and get some rest.

00:29:41.600 --> 00:29:43.530
Come back at 8 for the shift change.

00:29:43.850 --> 00:29:45.050
Where is Hu Wenjing?

00:29:45.590 --> 00:29:47.450
She went to the drug rehab center.

00:29:47.550 --> 00:29:48.030
Don't worry.

00:29:48.030 --> 00:29:49.630
Fengnan is covering for her.

00:29:50.710 --> 00:29:51.920
I'll head back now.

00:29:52.960 --> 00:29:54.420
Let's have some porridge.

00:29:56.750 --> 00:29:58.680
We'll have an apple after the meal.

00:29:58.920 --> 00:29:59.550
Right.

00:29:59.640 --> 00:30:00.790
Eat more.

00:30:00.790 --> 00:30:02.120
You'll be better soon.

00:30:03.440 --> 00:30:04.440
Good job, Jiang.

00:30:04.680 --> 00:30:06.140
Come on, let's have an egg.

00:30:08.030 --> 00:30:08.880
Xue.

00:30:08.990 --> 00:30:09.790
Hurry, hurry.

00:30:11.030 --> 00:30:11.750
What's wrong?

00:30:11.750 --> 00:30:12.990
He can't breathe again?

00:30:12.990 --> 00:30:13.470
It's okay, Jiang.

00:30:13.470 --> 00:30:14.070
Hold on.

00:30:14.070 --> 00:30:15.160
Lay him flat, he'll be fine.

00:30:15.160 --> 00:30:16.220
Lie down, lie down.

00:30:16.600 --> 00:30:17.360
Lie flat.

00:30:17.840 --> 00:30:18.640
It's okay.

00:30:21.360 --> 00:30:21.920
Hurry!

00:30:23.840 --> 00:30:24.510
Doctor!

00:30:24.920 --> 00:30:25.790
Doctor!

00:30:26.400 --> 00:30:27.660
Jiang, you'll be fine.

00:30:27.920 --> 00:30:28.790
Doctor!

00:30:29.790 --> 00:30:30.880
Doctor!

00:30:33.030 --> 00:30:33.880
Hurry!

00:30:34.070 --> 00:30:34.710
Quick!

00:30:35.200 --> 00:30:35.840
Quick!

00:31:00.710 --> 00:31:01.680
Li Xiaoya.

00:31:04.360 --> 00:31:05.360
You got a big car.

00:31:05.360 --> 00:31:06.620
Moving up in the world.

00:31:08.160 --> 00:31:09.550
I thought you said you weren't coming.

00:31:09.550 --> 00:31:11.550
I swapped shifts
with a colleague. I had to come.

00:31:11.550 --> 00:31:12.750
Why didn't you drive?

00:31:12.790 --> 00:31:13.990
I didn't sleep all night.

00:31:13.990 --> 00:31:15.850
I was afraid I couldn't handle it.

00:31:15.960 --> 00:31:16.960
Look at you.

00:31:17.030 --> 00:31:18.270
Why work so hard?

00:31:18.270 --> 00:31:19.030
What for?

00:31:19.170 --> 00:31:20.770
To get promoted and get rich.

00:31:21.120 --> 00:31:22.510
I believe the promotion part.

00:31:22.510 --> 00:31:23.120
But getting rich?

00:31:23.120 --> 00:31:24.880
Definitely not as rich as you.

00:31:25.550 --> 00:31:27.280
Let's go in. Just push the door.

00:31:28.470 --> 00:31:29.750
I saw your Moments.

00:31:29.750 --> 00:31:31.880
You're selling diet pills now, right?

00:31:32.070 --> 00:31:33.120
They're not pills.

00:31:33.120 --> 00:31:35.160
They're weight loss supplements.

00:31:35.160 --> 00:31:35.790
They sell really well.

00:31:35.790 --> 00:31:37.270
Give me two packs. I need to lose weight.

00:31:37.270 --> 00:31:38.270
Why do you need them?

00:31:38.270 --> 00:31:39.200
Do you need them?

00:31:39.470 --> 00:31:41.360
Are those diet pills harmful?

00:31:41.360 --> 00:31:42.360
No, they're not.

00:31:42.550 --> 00:31:44.680
They're just spirulina and vitamins.

00:31:45.600 --> 00:31:46.470
Do they work?

00:31:47.870 --> 00:31:49.200
You want me to be honest?

00:31:49.270 --> 00:31:50.070
No.

00:31:50.570 --> 00:31:51.840
And they still sell well?

00:31:51.840 --> 00:31:53.550
Who cares about results these days?

00:31:53.550 --> 00:31:54.760
It's all about advertising.

00:31:54.760 --> 00:31:55.490
There she is.

00:32:05.650 --> 00:32:05.840
[Xiekang Drug Rehabilitation Center
Police Office]

00:32:05.840 --> 00:32:07.620
Let's go. We'll take you home first.

00:32:07.620 --> 00:32:08.490
How was it?

00:32:10.160 --> 00:32:10.920
Not bad.

00:32:14.360 --> 00:32:15.640
I want to go on this.

00:32:18.130 --> 00:32:19.480
And this one.

00:32:21.120 --> 00:32:21.850
And this one.

00:32:22.640 --> 00:32:23.440
The carousel?

00:32:24.310 --> 00:32:24.850
Is that enough?

00:32:24.850 --> 00:32:25.710
That's enough.

00:32:26.830 --> 00:32:28.230
Let's add a Ferris wheel.

00:32:33.200 --> 00:32:34.030
And a roller coaster.

00:32:34.030 --> 00:32:34.710
A castle.

00:32:35.160 --> 00:32:36.160
Daddy.

00:32:36.960 --> 00:32:38.070
Wave.

00:32:38.440 --> 00:32:39.440
Wave.

00:33:26.990 --> 00:33:28.520
Look at how you're driving.

00:33:29.660 --> 00:33:31.460
What did they say at the factory?

00:33:32.550 --> 00:33:33.840
When I was in rehab,

00:33:33.840 --> 00:33:35.120
my boss called

00:33:35.620 --> 00:33:37.330
and said I was fired.

00:33:38.320 --> 00:33:39.470
About the job,

00:33:39.500 --> 00:33:40.260
it's fine.

00:33:40.310 --> 00:33:41.640
You can find another one.

00:33:41.640 --> 00:33:42.550
But drugs,

00:33:42.790 --> 00:33:44.720
you really can't touch them again.

00:33:45.640 --> 00:33:46.470
I know.

00:33:55.710 --> 00:33:57.510
Look at you, you've lost weight.

00:33:57.750 --> 00:33:59.120
Just go home and rest up.

00:33:59.120 --> 00:34:00.230
Eat some good food.

00:34:01.550 --> 00:34:04.440
Every time I took those pills before,

00:34:04.470 --> 00:34:06.200
I always felt like throwing up.

00:34:06.790 --> 00:34:07.790
I did lose some weight.

00:34:07.790 --> 00:34:09.719
But actually, in the rehab center,

00:34:09.800 --> 00:34:10.730
I was able to eat.

00:34:11.550 --> 00:34:13.030
Doesn't that stuff make everyone...

00:34:13.030 --> 00:34:13.630
Wang Ping,

00:34:13.630 --> 00:34:15.150
if you have trouble finding a job,

00:34:15.150 --> 00:34:16.810
come handle shipments for me.

00:34:18.989 --> 00:34:20.190
Let me think about it.

00:34:20.239 --> 00:34:21.070
It's okay, no rush.

00:34:21.070 --> 00:34:21.989
Take your time.

00:34:23.969 --> 00:34:26.449
You want her
to ship those diet pills, right?

00:34:27.280 --> 00:34:28.840
Someone we know is reliable.

00:34:28.840 --> 00:34:29.989
Besides, she's not doing anything.

00:34:29.989 --> 00:34:30.790
What's wrong?

00:34:31.469 --> 00:34:32.920
The lock won't open.

00:34:35.650 --> 00:34:36.980
Who are you looking for?

00:34:38.630 --> 00:34:39.540
Who are you?

00:34:41.550 --> 00:34:43.469
You must be friends of the previous owner.

00:34:43.469 --> 00:34:45.150
This apartment has been sold to me.

00:34:45.150 --> 00:34:46.630
If you're looking for the previous owner,

00:34:46.630 --> 00:34:47.510
you should call him directly.

00:34:47.510 --> 00:34:48.840
No, no, no, wait a minute.

00:34:48.840 --> 00:34:49.550
This is her home.

00:34:49.550 --> 00:34:50.290
Yeah.

00:34:50.320 --> 00:34:51.070
Her home?

00:34:51.070 --> 00:34:52.320
Yes, this is my home.

00:34:52.760 --> 00:34:53.880
That can't be.

00:34:54.300 --> 00:34:55.820
I saw the deed.

00:34:56.070 --> 00:34:57.440
His ID was there too.

00:34:57.720 --> 00:34:58.720
The owner is a man

00:34:58.720 --> 00:34:59.520
named Wang An.

00:34:59.670 --> 00:35:01.030
That's my brother.

00:35:02.190 --> 00:35:03.190
That explains it.

00:35:03.320 --> 00:35:04.470
He sold the house to me.

00:35:04.470 --> 00:35:05.510
The paperwork is done.

00:35:05.510 --> 00:35:06.550
It's all legal.

00:35:06.800 --> 00:35:08.320
And I've paid in full.

00:35:08.670 --> 00:35:10.030
If you have a problem,

00:35:10.030 --> 00:35:10.840
take it up with him.

00:35:10.840 --> 00:35:12.370
It has nothing to do with me.

00:35:20.450 --> 00:35:21.670
Wang An, that little bastard.

00:35:21.670 --> 00:35:22.800
He's such a scumbag.

00:35:23.070 --> 00:35:24.440
How could he, while you were inside,

00:35:24.440 --> 00:35:25.720
sell the house?

00:35:26.240 --> 00:35:28.040
I've never heard of such a thing.

00:35:28.510 --> 00:35:30.040
What an ungrateful wretch.

00:35:31.120 --> 00:35:33.580
It's normal that Wang An
couldn't accept it.

00:35:35.070 --> 00:35:36.280
Don't worry, Wang Ping.

00:35:36.280 --> 00:35:37.840
I can definitely find him for you.

00:35:37.840 --> 00:35:38.880
Just trust me.

00:35:38.880 --> 00:35:40.510
I'll bring him right to you.

00:35:41.280 --> 00:35:42.190
That's enough.

00:35:43.800 --> 00:35:44.880
Don't bother.

00:35:45.990 --> 00:35:47.120
In my current state,

00:35:47.640 --> 00:35:49.290
I'll just be a burden to him.

00:35:50.990 --> 00:35:53.400
Our bond as siblings might end here.

00:35:55.150 --> 00:35:57.350
I've taken care of him for so many years.

00:35:57.490 --> 00:35:59.890
I've done right by our late parents.

00:36:01.990 --> 00:36:02.920
Slow down.

00:36:06.800 --> 00:36:07.670
Wang Ping.

00:36:09.720 --> 00:36:10.760
You are

00:36:11.030 --> 00:36:12.630
only in your early thirties.

00:36:13.030 --> 00:36:14.800
You have plenty of good times ahead.

00:36:14.800 --> 00:36:16.440
While Wang An isn't here,

00:36:16.470 --> 00:36:17.550
think about your future.

00:36:17.550 --> 00:36:18.570
Whether he returns or not,

00:36:18.570 --> 00:36:19.630
you must live well.

00:36:19.760 --> 00:36:20.590
Trust me.

00:36:21.280 --> 00:36:22.670
Life is still very long.

00:36:22.990 --> 00:36:24.920
When you can take care of yourself,

00:36:24.960 --> 00:36:25.960
he will come back.

00:36:26.150 --> 00:36:28.280
Wang An needs to start his own life too.

00:36:28.880 --> 00:36:29.510
Exactly.

00:36:29.510 --> 00:36:30.610
That factory of yours

00:36:30.610 --> 00:36:31.640
was going to go under sooner or later.

00:36:31.640 --> 00:36:32.710
Getting out early now

00:36:32.710 --> 00:36:33.510
is even better.

00:36:33.510 --> 00:36:34.150
Really.

00:36:37.210 --> 00:36:39.600
I don't think you need
to rush to find a job.

00:36:39.960 --> 00:36:40.670
Take a break first.

00:36:40.670 --> 00:36:42.150
Let's plan this carefully.

00:36:42.150 --> 00:36:43.850
I happen to be going into the city too.

00:36:43.850 --> 00:36:45.760
I need to rent an apartment anyway.

00:36:45.760 --> 00:36:47.720
Why don't you stay with me
and clear your head?

00:36:47.720 --> 00:36:48.280
The two of us...

00:36:48.280 --> 00:36:48.840
That's enough.

00:36:48.840 --> 00:36:50.190
What are you doing?

00:36:51.070 --> 00:36:53.270
You don't need to worry about me so much.

00:36:53.570 --> 00:36:55.170
I won't do anything foolish.

00:36:56.510 --> 00:36:58.190
On the way over,

00:36:59.540 --> 00:37:00.870
I was thinking

00:37:02.990 --> 00:37:04.400
that maybe all this time,

00:37:05.280 --> 00:37:07.480
it wasn't Wang An who couldn't leave me.

00:37:09.280 --> 00:37:11.080
Maybe I was too dependent on him.

00:37:11.920 --> 00:37:12.630
Really.

00:37:13.030 --> 00:37:13.990
I also

00:37:14.190 --> 00:37:15.150
understand why you two

00:37:15.150 --> 00:37:17.220
kept telling me

00:37:17.360 --> 00:37:18.470
that he's grown up now,

00:37:18.470 --> 00:37:20.470
and I shouldn't manage him anymore.

00:37:20.550 --> 00:37:21.900
Now that he's suddenly left,

00:37:21.900 --> 00:37:23.010
I feel like

00:37:23.470 --> 00:37:24.670
I finally woke up.

00:37:27.070 --> 00:37:28.190
So rest assured.

00:37:29.410 --> 00:37:30.970
I won't do anything rash.

00:37:32.060 --> 00:37:33.460
I don't owe him anything.

00:37:35.630 --> 00:37:36.070
Exactly.

00:37:36.070 --> 00:37:36.920
As long as you think that way.

00:37:36.920 --> 00:37:38.980
We're relieved if you think that way.

00:37:39.030 --> 00:37:41.030
When Hu Wenjing told me to slow down,

00:37:41.040 --> 00:37:42.030
I was scared you were going
to do something rash.

00:37:42.030 --> 00:37:42.960
I was terrified.

00:37:43.800 --> 00:37:45.600
I simply wanted you to slow down.

00:37:45.620 --> 00:37:46.140
Really?

00:37:46.190 --> 00:37:46.800
Yes.

00:37:47.590 --> 00:37:48.800
I overthought it.

00:37:49.510 --> 00:37:50.880
This is great, really.

00:37:50.880 --> 00:37:53.140
You have to remember what you said today.

00:37:53.240 --> 00:37:54.470
When that little bastard Wang An

00:37:54.470 --> 00:37:55.670
comes back looking for you,

00:37:55.670 --> 00:37:56.720
you can't go soft on him.

00:37:56.720 --> 00:37:57.150
Right.

00:37:57.150 --> 00:37:58.210
Do you understand?

00:37:58.760 --> 00:37:59.720
Okay.

00:38:02.280 --> 00:38:03.840
I'll try to start over.

00:38:04.110 --> 00:38:04.800
Yes.

00:38:05.030 --> 00:38:06.760
You should learn to enjoy life.

00:38:08.360 --> 00:38:09.070
How is it?

00:38:09.430 --> 00:38:10.430
Does it feel good?

00:38:29.890 --> 00:38:30.770
It smells a bit.

00:38:30.960 --> 00:38:32.490
Because it's full of goods.

00:38:32.920 --> 00:38:34.070
This is the bedroom.

00:38:36.100 --> 00:38:37.290
There's no bedding yet.

00:38:37.290 --> 00:38:39.020
I'll set it all up for you later.

00:38:39.880 --> 00:38:41.400
When you have nothing to do,

00:38:41.400 --> 00:38:42.920
you can learn how to ship orders.

00:38:42.920 --> 00:38:44.650
Just treat it as a distraction.

00:38:47.760 --> 00:38:49.440
Haven't I been to this apartment before?

00:38:49.440 --> 00:38:50.900
It was empty before, right?

00:38:50.900 --> 00:38:51.820
Yes.

00:38:51.850 --> 00:38:53.550
Because we couldn't
fit anything else downstairs,

00:38:53.550 --> 00:38:55.190
so I set this place up.

00:38:55.790 --> 00:38:56.550
Where is Cheng Xiaodong?

00:38:56.550 --> 00:38:57.590
He went fishing.

00:38:58.030 --> 00:38:59.760
He's been working hard
shipping orders these past few days,

00:38:59.760 --> 00:39:00.960
so I gave him a day off.

00:39:01.680 --> 00:39:03.430
Are these your diet pills?

00:39:04.800 --> 00:39:06.270
This is the only product
I'm selling right now.

00:39:06.270 --> 00:39:06.800
Give me one.

00:39:06.800 --> 00:39:08.640
I'll take it back
and lose some weight too.

00:39:08.640 --> 00:39:09.670
You don't need to lose weight.

00:39:09.670 --> 00:39:10.800
You're so thin.

00:39:10.880 --> 00:39:11.840
Didn't I just tell you?

00:39:11.840 --> 00:39:12.880
It doesn't work anyway.

00:39:12.880 --> 00:39:14.190
You sell it even if it doesn't work?

00:39:14.190 --> 00:39:15.590
As long as it makes money.

00:39:15.810 --> 00:39:16.720
You guys stay here.

00:39:16.720 --> 00:39:17.920
I'll go down and get her
some daily necessities.

00:39:17.920 --> 00:39:18.360
Okay.

00:39:18.920 --> 00:39:19.470
Xiaoya.

00:39:19.760 --> 00:39:21.020
Where is the bathroom?

00:39:21.510 --> 00:39:21.890
Here.

00:39:44.280 --> 00:39:44.920
Wang Ping.

00:39:46.510 --> 00:39:48.370
I need to rush back to the station.

00:39:48.400 --> 00:39:50.240
Tell Xiaoya when she gets back.

00:39:50.390 --> 00:39:50.950
Okay.

00:39:51.030 --> 00:39:53.070
Call me if anything happens.

00:39:54.320 --> 00:39:55.050
I'm leaving.

00:40:02.520 --> 00:40:11.600
[Next Episode Preview]